on of yields from a massive Population III object and a normal Type\nII SN. These scenarios provide important information on the C production in the\nearly Universe, and on the formation of C-rich stars in the early Galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Dec 2006 19:35:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
