 their main stage of\nmass-building. The characteristics of the 2-4$\\mu$m spectra are placed in the\ncontext of existing multi-wavelength data, and five of the stars are more\nconsistent with reddened Class IIs or stars in transition between Class I and\nII, rather than protostars embedded within massive remnant envelopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Dec 2006 01:35:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
